high_descs: Move to stand in front of the black desk, facing the open laptop.
Pick up the gray bowl from the desk that's next to the box.
Move directly in front of that open box on the table while carrying the bowl.
Place the bowl inside the box on the desk.
Pick up the box with the bowl in it from the desk.
Carry the box with the bowl in it to the coffee table.
Place the box with the bowl in it on the coffee table, behind the sculpture and on the edge closest to the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Move a box with a bowl inside to the coffee table.

high_descs: Step forward, turn left, move forward, then turn right to approach the desk.
Pick up the vase on the desk, next to the box.
Move to the right of the desk.
Put the vase in the box on the desk.
Pick up the box with the vase in it.
Turn right, go forward, then turn right to approach the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table, behind the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a vase in it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then turn to face the black desk.
Pick up the black bowl from the desk.
Move right and turn to face the desk.
Put the bowl in the box.
Pick the box up from the desk.
Turn right and then right again to face the glass table.
Put the box on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a bowl in it on a table.
